{"title":"docker安装gitlab","date":"2021-01-25T10:24:22.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 25, 2021","L":"01/25/2021","MM-DD":"01-25"},"link":"2021/01/25/docker-install-gitlab","tags":["gitlab"],"categories":["gitlab"],"updated":"2021-01-25T10:55:01.236Z","content":"<p>搜索gitlab</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker search gitlab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>拉取gitlab镜像，其中gitlab-ce为社区版，gitlab-ee为企业版，这里我们拉取社区版即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull gitlab/gitlab-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>运行gitlab-ce容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -p 443:443 -p 80:80 -p 222:22 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --restart always \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /etc/gitlab:/etc/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /var/<span class=\"built_in\">log</span>/gitlab:/var/<span class=\"built_in\">log</span>/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /var/opt/gitlab:/var/opt/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gitlab/gitlab-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-v /etc/gitlab:/etc/gitlab</code> 配置文件目录映射</li>\n<li><code>-v /var/log/gitlab:/var/log/gitlab</code> 日志文件目录映射到</li>\n<li><code>-v /var/opt/gitlab:/var/opt/gitlab</code> 数据文件目录映射</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em><strong>nginx等服务的默认端口都为80，如果安装了nginx，记得修改80的端口映射</strong></em></p>\n</blockquote>\n","next":{"title":"docker安装jenkins","link":"2021/01/21/docker-install-jenkins"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2021/01/25/docker-install-gitlab/","reward":true}